lead_paragraph: Thomas Meunier volleyed a spectacular last-minute goal to give Paris St Germain a 2-1 win at FC Basel, which took them into the last 16 of the Champions League on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: PSG Snatch Last-Gasp Win and Knockout Stage Place
